{"tid":1202556,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史學] 60億圓紙幣","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:10:52.000Z","uid":35070,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dac9714cffa1ac1bd3fece218a1c298d8f208afb","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4e/Six_billion_banknote_ROC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4e%2FSix_billion_banknote_ROC.jpg&h=95552fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n60億圓紙幣於1949年5月10日，由中華民國新疆省銀行發行，是中國歷史上面額最大的紙幣。<br />\n這張60億圓的鈔票上，印有「折合金圓券壹萬圓」字樣，這也是中國貨幣史上唯一在一枚紙幣上並列兩種不同的貨幣單位和金額的紙幣。<br />\n在當時，這張紙幣的價值，只折合77粒至88粒白米。"},{"pid":"11ab1c277d58c1b8856087143fa4105099e1ba9b","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:38:24.000Z","msg":"歷史<br />\n1948年8月，中華民國政府發行的法幣因通貨膨脹而徹底崩潰，於是發行新的貨幣金圓券，並以1押300萬法幣的比價收兌舊幣。<br />\n由於未能嚴守發行限制，新貨幣無助抑制物價上漲，惡性通貨膨脹持續，百姓深受其害。<br />\n當時，中央政府發行的貨幣與新疆地方貨幣折價共同流通使用。<br />\n<br />\n1948年12月，新疆商業銀行改組為新疆省銀行，其後發行<span style=\"color: red;\">3000萬圓、6000萬圓、6億圓和30億圓</span>的銀行券作為地方貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n到1949年5月，該行發行了面值<span style=\"color: red;\">60億圓</span>的銀行券，成為中國史上面額最大的紙幣。"},{"pid":"53272a6dc9f1bf6cdee56645a8a5e987290a7a59","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"市值<br />\n這張60億圓的鈔票，在當時只值0.01銀元，即銀0.00648兩。按當時上海一石白米的價格是金圓券4.4億元計算，這張60億圓紙幣只能買到88粒米。<br />\n（又另一種計法，根據當時上海金圓券130元僅能夠買一粒米的行情，這張60億圓紙幣只能買到約77粒米。）"},{"pid":"477374a218845f0e9d09ba610fb6bf818afa3f2b","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"資料來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/60%E5%84%84%E5%9C%93%E7%B4%99%E5%B9%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F60%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%259C%2593%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B9%25A3&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo5qf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=9a4116d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/60%E5%84%84%E5%9C%93%E7%B4%99%E5%B9%A3</a>"},{"pid":"65da8b9e6d4e575dd00d659f84822d5086762ff2","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://data.shouxi.com/upload/img/0e/fb/0efb6910ad28c17d667c8fcbc17cb1d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdata.shouxi.com%2Fupload%2Fimg%2F0e%2Ffb%2F0efb6910ad28c17d667c8fcbc17cb1d4.jpg&h=374a0fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"530ff520b6ced813ee743bb43c7faf42c097571d","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b84fdae5c0fa1be9d60a2e5ff321ad2d39a965","tid":1202556,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fa29d730abe0e743f3ad13c2c8f2a1d30dcd1e","tid":1202556,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}